snippet.title: Evan and Katelyn
snippet.description:
Hi, we're Evan and Katelyn Heling and we make stuff together: woodworking, 3D printing, welding, props, CNC, home projects, sometimes practical stuff, sometimes totally unnecessary but fun stuff.

The reason we started this channel is partly for y'all, but partly for us too. We want to show that making stuff is fun and accessible, even if you're figuring it out as you go (like we often are). But also, we wanna work together. We're basically each others favorite person, and being able to do stuff we love with the person we love is pretty much the dream.

We have more channels too!
🎮 Our gaming channel https://www.youtube.com/evanandkatelyngaming
🎙️ Our podcast https://www.youtube.com/evanandkatelynpodcast
📺 Our 2nd channel https://www.youtube.com/evanandkatelyn2
🎮 We stream at https://www.twitch.tv/evanandkatelyn 

Below is our mailing address. If you're a business, please do NOT send unsolicited products:

Evan and Katelyn
215 W Bandera Rd Ste 114-240
Boerne, TX 78006
